{"tid":1679785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者請入：點解一定要出席警方記者會？","createTime":"2019-10-28T11:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T12:54:25.000Z","uid":305005,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"92d5c065e8e1124b5e737d18a989444d396b6c97","tid":1679785,"uid":305005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">面對記者市民被不公平對待 為表抗議 點解唔行動 一齊杯葛個記者會？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以試下同公司傾下<br />\n<br />\n市民有知情權 但唔係聽依d警察偏頗既言論 有幾多次警察當人傻仔（yellow object 都講得出）加上政府已有好多平台發佈消息<br />\n<br />\n當警察仲有公信力都可以聽下 ，但當佢而家公信力咁低，聽完寫番出黎比市民睇 只不過係散播不良消息比市民<br />\n<br />\n同埋不合理對待完你地記者，你地都照出席佢地記完會（合哂佢地心意），同一時間警方又唔駛為自己行為負責，記者待遇係唔會有改善（因為一個願打一個願捱[/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n所以最好聯同幾個報社一齊杯葛警方記者會 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">比一個訊息佢地 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">警察唔係大哂 你地唔尊重記者 記者都唔會尊重你</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"4faea8d738a95d237fbc58cc92b29dd9785361fb","tid":1679785,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6bd0fcf50bbf215988100f51f43de996dbb87624","tid":1679785,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"唔出席<br />\n就會變cctv x 大公報 新華社 聯合popo發佈會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd59fc3f3855d6f741e8d8cfaff1aded96e4a1a","tid":1679785,"uid":130695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s